1. *Sredim* ga još danas (I will fix him today).
2. On će sama *srediti* situaciju (She will sort out the situation herself).
3. Ono što treba da *sredimo* je naše učenje (What we need to sort out is our studying).
4. *Sredimo* sada sve te stvari (Let's sort out all those things now).
5. Ona će *srediti* svoje stvari (She will arrange her things). 
6. Moramo da *sredimo* svoje živote (We have to arrange our lives).